data.description:
Welcome to the charm and character of 509 Bostwick Avenue, a delightful residence nestled in the sought-after Bostwick Park subdivision in Daytona Beach, Volusia County. This meticulously maintained single-family home, built in 1953, presents a unique opportunity to own a spacious beachside home. Boasting 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, this Florida-style gem offers a warm and inviting atmosphere.As you step inside this well laid out home, you'll be greeted by the timeless beauty of tile and wood flooring, complemented by cathedral and vaulted ceilings that enhance the spaciousness of the home. The fireplace adds just the right touch of charm and coziness to the living space.  The interior is adorned with charming details, making it a perfect blend of functionality and aesthetics. This home is close to all the amenities Daytona Beach has to offer like its World-Famous Beaches, events, Daytona Internationa Speedway, The Hard Rock, and much more.
Embrace the Florida lifestyle and call this meticulously designed residence at 509 Bostwick Avenue your next Home.
